title: To my girlfriend
text:
Hey B,
Hate that you have an emotionally heavy day ahead of you. They are fortunate, as am I, to have a thoughtful, caring, emotionally intelligent nurse taking care of them today.
Keeping you in my thoughts. I love you very much.
Your blogger boyfriend,
Cyrus
